snippet.title: Conbunn Cardboard - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Conbunn Cardboard is a chill and cozy platformer. Hop around collecting the lost CDs of a cute DJ in this land made of cardboard!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2004590/Conbunn_Cardboard/

Conbunn Cardboard Discord Server: https://discord.gg/NaK6sBW4mB
